  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Ninneko Clan, level 8+ <br />Your lifeforce is tenacious and your luck is immeasurable! You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>You halve the additional damage that would be dealt as a result of a critical hit against you.</li><li>You gain an additional use of your <em><strong>Nine Lives</strong></em> clan feature.</li><li>You may spend a use of this feature as a reaction when you fail a saving throw against a hostile effect to instead succeed. When you succeed a saving throw this way, you are not subject to any further of its effects.</li></ul>",
